    <h1 class="p-4 my-5 custom-title" style="font-size: 80px; font-weight: 700;">Phonenumber</h1>
    <h4 class="text-center mt-4 mb-5">Use this package with phone number field. validate if number is correct.</h4>
    <br>
    <hr />
    <h2 class="my-5 custom-title">Install the package</h2>
    <div class="mt-2"></div>
    <pre class="mb-5">
        <code class="language-Django">
            pip install django-phonenumber-field
            pip install django-phonenumbers
            <span></span>
        </code>
    </pre>
    <hr />
    <h4 class="mb-4 mt-5">Insert the package into INSTALLED_APPS list.</h4>
    <pre class="mb-5">
        <code class="language-Django">
            INSTALLED_APPS = [
                ...
                "phonenumber_field",
            ]
            <span></span>
        </code>
    </pre>
    <hr />
    <h4 class="mb-4 mt-5">Use it in the model.</h4>
    <pre class="mb-5">
        <code class="language-Django">
            from phonenumber_field.modelfields import PhoneNumberField
            phone_number = PhoneNumberField()
            <span></span>
        </code>
    </pre>

